Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你
