Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.83,0:02:52.25,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}嚎哭的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见吗 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的爆炸声是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在 强袭和空中霸王2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰船受损状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里等下去不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛多克上士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题不严重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对能量供应管进行下应急处理就能飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是咱们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下再被拿去利用算什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6…6点方向 雷达发现机影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是DINN 预测15分钟后遇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在半数以上火器瘫痪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对3架DINN 10分钟也坚持不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答 DINN…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和少尉和凯尼二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部MIA了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认定为MIA吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,missing in action
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有确认 不过大概战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不看开 下个死的就是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DINN接近 11分钟后遇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量供应恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升空 推进力最大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升空 推进力最大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号机和强袭最后的位置是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7点方向小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下不可能再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校的1号机呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 还没法出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 不走死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉和多尔都成功逃生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿拉斯加总部联系上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要全体船员去送死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 把小岛位置和求救信号发给奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是人员救助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 让那个国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任由我来负！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DINN接近 距离8000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大功率 优先离开空域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撤吗 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIA什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰和提亚哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船在移动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接到克鲁泽队长的返航命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体情况没人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们首先和暴风失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一次巨大的爆炸后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和神盾也失去了联系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求救信号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有发出过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭和长腿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波斯曼队正在追击长腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上让船调头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不可能轻易被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身红不是白穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该能冷静判断情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们奉命返航
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他部队会负责搜寻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消息说奥布也出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的机体自爆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以强袭也被…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去 卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:09:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空的 可能被吹飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是逃离了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城坂一校 对面海滩上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是奥布的飞艇里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发现晕倒在海滩上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行了救治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中立的奥布想要我怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别告诉我你现在是地球军了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掉强袭的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你一样逃脱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都找不到 基拉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经…被我杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我 亲手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用神盾缠住 自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太可能逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是唯一的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打败他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为当时逃出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是因为你想亲手杀我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉他 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总让人担心 想法古怪 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还喜欢哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很善良 是个好人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前就是这么个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱哭虫 喜欢撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优秀却做事随随便便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识 不但认识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小 就是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么还要杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分开后 再见面就是敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好几次劝他过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是调整人 是我们这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在地球军才不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他就是不听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:14:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗中杀了我们的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了尼科尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就杀了基拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人了！他已经
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么办法？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非要变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了尼科尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了那个喜欢弹钢琴 才刚15岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了保护PLANT参军的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉也是为保护身边的人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他难道就应该被杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是被你这个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被杀所以去杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为杀人所以被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样最后真的能和平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色领导者防卫队来电
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我部就此返航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们感谢掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18号雷达站要求对照船籍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是初次入驻阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传送数据 应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防卫队再晚来一步就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过DINN撤得也真快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区3架冲进防空圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面没傻到想跟阿拉斯加过不去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯加就那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有聊够？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是二级战斗状态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半舷轮休
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除二级战斗状态 半舷轮休
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长也来劝劝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈少校非要我们把机体修好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是加挂燃料去找那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允许你去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让维护班歇息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布还没消息来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船已经安全了 有什么关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不批准
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他们 如果真的还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 可能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也恨不得现在就飞去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不能让少校单独去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连你也一去不回 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有相信奥布和基拉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿盖尔二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把凯尼二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大和少尉的遗物整理出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗物？可是还…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长已经认定MIA 这是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉迷于感伤的话 下个死的就是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 丢了强袭回到阿拉斯加也真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到大和会挂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兹 基拉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战时失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队里 指未经确认的战死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细的问其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是问 基拉人在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不知道 连是死是活也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？基拉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔有消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不过没事的 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长已经委托奥布找人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到总部说不定就有消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一个人待在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 别推推搡搡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是伤号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 把人家晾在一边不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暴风的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这艘船上还有这么嫩的妹子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻不傻 哭什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对俘虏施暴是被禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接他的人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 接你的人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把扎夫特的军人带去奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说谢谢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知该如何是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哈乌梅亚的守护石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太不让人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知我杀了基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再看到任何人死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 还有脸回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉强袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是坏孩子 小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不可以让你乱玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小粉红 不可以去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自怀着伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找治愈之所 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徘徊的心或是消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是失控
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今抵达的是何处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想的世界再次被阴影笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这就是时代 人们会…
